data.description: Welcome to this charming brick bungalow, with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 1-car detached garage. The first floor contains 2 bedrooms and full bath. Upstairs, you'll find a large 3rd bedroom suite and half bath that is the entire second floor. If you are an investor this is a great rental as there is no HOA and monthly rental prices in the area are anywhere from $850 for 2 bedrooms to $1100. Come and check out this home before its gone!
